snippet.description:
I got bored as fuck in self isolation & quarantine and my wifey and I crushed every episode of Tiger King in one sitting. I became obsessed to the point I was looking up people from the show on Facebook. It got so bad and I got so bored that this happened. Carole killed her husband.

Merch: https://shopkt8merch.com/collections/merkules

Produced by Nigel Childs
Filmed by Carissa Bell
Edited by Lil Windex
Mixed and Mastered by @mixedbybrandon 

#TigerKing
snippet.title: Merkules - ''Carole Killed Her Husband'' (Joe Exotic Remix) #TigerKing
